headline: Jack Henry & Associates Announces Regular Quarterly Dividend
summary: Jack Henry & Associates, Inc. (NASDAQ: JKHY) today announced its Board of Directors declared a regular quarterly cash dividend of $.58 per share. The cash dividend on its common stock, par value $.01 per share, is payable on June 18, 2025, to stockholders of record as of May 29, 2025.
